PrecisAuthority for the CANADA PORTS CORPORATION (a) to ACQUIRE TITLE from the Crown with respect to the real property associated with the PORT OF CHURCHILL in Manitoba, and (b) to enter into AGREEMENTS with the HUDSON BAY PORT COMPANY, the Minister of Transport, OmniTRAX Canada Inc., OmniTRAX, INC., the Minister of Public Works and Government Services, the TOWN OF CHURCHILL and THE MANITOBA HYDRO-ELECTRIC BOARD respecting the sale of the real property and other tangible assets associated with the Port.
